                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer>A Countryman</trailer>
                <names/>
                <summary>"A Countryman" writes again, taking exception to the personal insults he
                    feels he has received from "Z," and retorts with banter of his own against "Z.".
                    He argues that he does not dislike lawyers, but actually has respect for the
                    profession.</summary>
                <note/>
