                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Editorial discussing the travails of Senator Stephen Douglas and the
                    disfavor in which he is held by most members of his party. Despite such
                    antipathy, the Democrats will probably nominate Douglas because he is such a
                    skillful politician.</summary>
                <note/>
