                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Authors claim that they know that James Lilley will not have the current
                    Sheriff or any of his deputies on his staff if he becomes Sheriff, and they
                    advocate his election.</summary>
                <note/>
            </div>
