                <head>Requisition for Merriam and Brown</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Governor Letcher expresses his outrage toward Governor Dennison of Ohio for
                    refusing Letcher's request for arrest and extradition of Francis Merriam and
                    Oliver Brown, two men suspected of participating in John Brown's Raid.</summary>
                <note/>
